data.description: This stunning home is nestled in the prestigious Tuscany GATED community! Boasting an array of remarkable features including OWNED Solar, a water softener and ceiling fans. Stepping through the courtyard entry with a charming gate, you are greeted by a sense of privacy and elegance. Inside, the home opens to a spacious formal living and dining room. The kitchen features an upgraded Quartz island w/ bar top seating. The adjacent den is a cozy retreat, complete w/ a fireplace and an abundance of natural light. The primary bedroom and ensuite bath features a separate tub, walk-in shower, dual vanities, and a spacious walk-in closet. Including an additional bedroom with its own private bath. 2 additional bedrooms, a hall bath and utility room complete the layout. Outside, you'll discover a covered patio that provides a shaded outdoor oasis for relaxation and entertainment. The partially gated yard is adorned with a variety of trees, creating a picturesque view and setting. Call today!
